<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>The Ultimate Typography Matrix</title>
    
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Antonio:wght@700&family=Bricolage+Grotesque:wght@800;900&family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500&family=Inter:wght@400;500;700&family=Oswald:wght@600;700&family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;600&family=Public+Sans:wght@400;600&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;700&family=Syncopate:wght@700&family=Syne:wght@700;800&family=Unbounded:wght@800;900&family=Urbanist:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    colors: {
                        bone: '#F3F3E9',
                        cinnabar: '#E33529',
                        cherub: '#F4CED3',
                        skyblue: '#AFD8FB',
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    </script>

    <style>
        /* Font Utility Map */
        .font-antonio { font-family: 'Antonio', sans-serif; }
        .font-urbanist { font-family: 'Urbanist', sans-serif; }
        
        .font-syncopate { font-family: 'Syncopate', sans-serif; }
        .font-inter { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }
        
        .font-unbounded { font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif; }
        .font-jakarta { font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; }
        
        .font-syne { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; }
        .font-space { font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif; }
        
        .font-oswald { font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif; }
        .font-dmsans { font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; }
        
        .font-bricolage { font-family: 'Bricolage Grotesque', sans-serif; }
        .font-public { font-family: 'Public Sans', sans-serif; }

        /* Fluid Sizing Engines */
        .fluid-display {
            font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 7vw + 1rem, 10rem);
            line-height: 0.85;
        }
        .fluid-body {
            font-size: clamp(0.875rem, 1vw + 0.5rem, 1.1rem);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-bone text-neutral-900 overflow-x-hidden relative selection:bg-cinnabar selection:text-white antialiased">

    <div class="fixed inset-0 pointer-events-none z-50 opacity-[0.04] mix-blend-multiply">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-full h-full">
            <filter id="canvasNoise">
                <feTurbulence type="fractalNoise" baseFrequency="0.8" numOctaves="4" stitchTiles="stitch" />
            </filter>
            <rect width="100%" height="100%" filter="url(#canvasNoise)" />
        </svg>
    </div>

    <header class="sticky top-0 w-full bg-bone/90 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-neutral-950/10 z-40 px-[4vw] py-4 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start md:items-center gap-4">
        <div>
            <h1 class="font-space text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-neutral-900">The Typography Playground</h1>
            <p class="font-inter text-[10px] text-neutral-500 uppercase tracking-wider mt-0.5">6 Curation Frameworks for Live Event Watercoloring</p>
        </div>
        <nav class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-6 gap-y-2 font-space text-[10px] font-bold tracking-widest text-neutral-600">
            <a href="#opt1" class="hover:text-cinnabar transition-colors">01. COMPRESSED</a>
            <a href="#opt2" class="hover:text-cinnabar transition-colors">02. EXTENDED</a>
            <a href="#opt3" class="hover:text-cinnabar transition-colors">03. HEAVY KINETIC</a>
            <a href="#opt4" class="hover:text-cinnabar transition-colors">04. AVANT-GARDE</a>
            <a href="#opt5" class="hover:text-cinnabar transition-colors">05. STARK IMPACT</a>
            <a href="#opt6" class="hover:text-cinnabar transition-colors">06. NEO-EDITORIAL</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <section id="opt1" class="w-screen min-h-[90vh] py-24 px-[6vw] border-b border-neutral-950/10 flex flex-col justify-between">
        <span class="font-space text-[10px] tracking-[0.22em] text-cinnabar font-bold uppercase mb-8">[ OPTION 01 — ANTONIO + URBANIST ]</span>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-6 items-start my-auto">
            <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-8">
                <h2 class="font-antonio fluid-display uppercase font-bold tracking-tighter text-neutral-950">
                    MAPPING <br>THE LIVE <br><span class="text-cinnabar">PIGMENT</span>.
                </h2>
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-6 lg:col-span-4 lg:mt-12">
                <p class="font-urbanist fluid-body font-medium leading-relaxed text-neutral-700 mb-6">
                    A highly dense, narrow editorial framework designed to mirror premium fashion lookbooks. Text acts as stark vertical anchors across the canvas layout.
                </p>
                <div class="w-12 h-[3px] bg-neutral-950"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="opt2" class="w-screen min-h-[90vh] py-24 px-[6vw] border-b border-neutral-950/10 bg-neutral-950 text-bone flex flex-col justify-between">
        <span class="font-space text-[10px] tracking-[0.22em] text-skyblue font-bold uppercase mb-8">[ OPTION 02 — SYNCOPATE + INTER ]</span>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-6 items-center my-auto">
            <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-7">
                <h2 class="font-syncopate fluid-display uppercase font-bold tracking-tight text-bone">
                    FLUID <br><span class="text-cherub">WASH</span>.
                </h2>
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-6 lg:col-span-5 border-l border-bone/20 pl-6 lg:pl-12">
                <p class="font-inter fluid-body font-light leading-relaxed text-neutral-300">
                    Ultra-wide structural alignments that occupy wide horizontal spaces perfectly. Gives package grids and timelines an expensive gallery feel.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="opt3" class="w-screen min-h-[90vh] py-24 px-[6vw] border-b border-neutral-950/10 flex flex-col justify-between">
        <span class="font-space text-[10px] tracking-[0.22em] text-cinnabar font-bold uppercase mb-8">[ OPTION 03 — UNBOUNDED + PLUS JAKARTA SANS ]</span>
        <div class="w-full my-auto">
            <h2 class="font-unbounded fluid-display uppercase font-bold tracking-tighter text-neutral-950 mb-12">
                STUDIO <br>CAPTURE
            </h2>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-6">
                <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-4 bg-cherub p-6 border-2 border-neutral-950">
                    <p class="font-jakarta text-xs md:text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-900 leading-relaxed">
                        Thick, loud geometric weight balanced flawlessly by a neutral, friendly body typeface. Great for making bold modular section blocks.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="opt4" class="w-screen min-h-[90vh] py-24 px-[6vw] border-b border-neutral-950/10 flex flex-col justify-between">
        <span class="font-space text-[10px] tracking-[0.22em] text-neutral-500 font-bold uppercase mb-8">[ OPTION 04 — SYNE + SPACE GROTESK ]</span>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-6 items-end my-auto">
            <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-9">
                <h2 class="font-syne fluid-display uppercase font-extrabold tracking-tighter text-neutral-950">
                    The Curation <br><span class="text-cinnabar">Timeline</span>
                </h2>
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-6 lg:col-span-3">
                <p class="font-space fluid-body font-normal leading-relaxed text-neutral-600">
                    Experimental curves meet sharp technical mono-leaning details. Excellent configuration if you want to stand apart from any typical wedding layout template.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="opt5" class="w-screen min-h-[90vh] py-24 px-[6vw] border-b border-neutral-950/10 bg-neutral-900 text-bone flex flex-col justify-between">
        <span class="font-space text-[10px] tracking-[0.22em] text-cherub font-bold uppercase mb-8">[ OPTION 05 — OSWALD + DM SANS ]</span>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-6 items-start my-auto">
            <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-6">
                <h2 class="font-oswald fluid-display uppercase font-bold tracking-tight text-white">
                    FINE ART <br>DELIVERY
                </h2>
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-6 lg:col-span-5 lg:col-start-8">
                <p class="font-dmsans fluid-body font-normal leading-relaxed text-neutral-300">
                    A heavy, clean mid-century industrial vibe. Strips away artistic eccentricity in favor of ultra-clean structure, framing your paintings like legendary museum pieces.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="opt6" class="w-screen min-h-[90vh] py-24 px-[6vw] flex flex-col justify-between">
        <span class="font-space text-[10px] tracking-[0.22em] text-cinnabar font-bold uppercase mb-8">[ OPTION 06 — BRICOLAGE GROTESQUE + PUBLIC SANS ]</span>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-6 items-center my-auto">
            <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-8">
                <h2 class="font-bricolage fluid-display uppercase font-black tracking-tighter text-neutral-950">
                    Archival <br><span class="text-cinnabar">Standard</span>
                </h2>
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-6 lg:col-span-4 bg-skyblue p-8 border border-neutral-900/20">
                <p class="font-public fluid-body font-medium leading-relaxed text-neutral-900">
                    Full of personality, ink-traps, and contemporary quirks. It looks incredibly intentional when contrasted with clean, structured corporate body layouts.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

</body>
</html>
